{
  "stem": "23350.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] now the gates were closed, and we are standing outside, and we didn't know what they were going to do with us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had to stand like soldiers, with no-- nothing to drink.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mouth was-- all of us-- dry, and the sun was really burning our heads, no-- no-- no-- shaved heads.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, we had two German women who were in charge of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were going in and out, and until they went, until they came out-- hours were-- we were standing and-- and not knowing still what they're going to do with us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was getting dusk, they opened the gates, and they let us in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no crematorium going that day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If the crematorium would be going that day, well, we wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this happened to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was the first time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was when I was separated with my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My sister never believed, ever, that she will ever see me alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I had hoped that, because she was sent to work, that I might see her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But anyway, we-- on another selection-- it was past another few weeks and I wasn't selected.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was put in a dark room in the corner of the barrack there, in-- in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I didn't know what's going to happen to us now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It so happens it was 1944, and by that time, whether it was September, October-- maybe middle of September or something-- that the crematoriums were going, still going, but certain days, yes, certain.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And in any case, they weren't going to-- to do the-- the gas for-- unless they had a big transport.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
